WEBVTT

00:00:00.794 --> 00:00:01.960
Obožavam modu.

00:00:02.693 --> 00:00:06.622
Svake večeri odlazim u krevet
i razmišljam što ću odjenuti

00:00:06.646 --> 00:00:07.865
sljedećeg dana.

00:00:08.549 --> 00:00:10.992
Odjeća me mijenja,

00:00:11.016 --> 00:00:12.578
određuje,

00:00:12.602 --> 00:00:14.052
čini me samouvjerenom.

00:00:14.769 --> 00:00:17.356
Možda nemate jednak stav prema modi,

00:00:17.380 --> 00:00:23.702
ali sigurno imate omiljenu majicu
ili traperice koje vas čine drugačijima --

00:00:23.726 --> 00:00:25.253
u kojima se osjećate dobro,

00:00:25.277 --> 00:00:27.006
u kojima se osjećate samouvjereno

00:00:27.030 --> 00:00:28.649
i posebno.

00:00:29.480 --> 00:00:31.202
Kada sam bila mlađa,